Package: botscan
Type: Package
Title: Scans Twitter Conversations For Bots
Version: 1.0.2
Author: Kurt Wirth
Maintainer: Kurt Wirth <KurtAWirth@gmail.com>
Description: This package accepts any Twitter search query as an input and
    outputs the percentage of the conversation 's tweets that are
    predicted to be authored by non-humans, or "bots". This tool uses rtweets 
    to search Twitter and botrnot and its machine learning technique to analyze 
    handles.IMPORTANT - In order to install this package, you must first install 
    botrnot from https://github.com/mkearney/botrnot.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports:
    rtweet,
    botrnot,
    dplyr
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
Suggests: testthat
